data.description: Welcome to your sanctuary in Saint Cloud, where convenience meets tranquility, and the journey to your dream lifestyle begins. From the moment you step through the front door, the ambiance of sophistication envelops you, guided by the contemporary allure of wood plank porcelain flooring that graces the entire main floor. The lower level of this meticulously maintained property unfolds seamlessly, beginning with a versatile studio/office space, ideal for those who appreciate a dedicated workspace. The formal dining area, adorned with a modern finish chandelier, sets the stage for memorable gatherings, while the adjacent modern kitchen is a culinary masterpiece.  The kitchen not only boasts top-notch stainless steel appliances but also features a generously sized pantry with upgraded shelves, providing ample storage for your culinary essentials.  A touch of sophistication is added to the kitchen with an inviting bar, designed for both utility and style. This upgraded bar is equipped with a sink, adding convenience to your entertaining. Imagine hosting guests or enjoying a casual breakfast or a coffee with the ease of access to a fully equipped bar. Delving into the finer details, the bar cabinets are designed with ingenuity in mind. They provide discreet space for robotic cleaning devices, allowing them to seamlessly navigate in and out of their storage haven, cleverly hidden from sight when not in use. Revel in the upgraded island featuring pop-up outlets and a waterfall-style counter that elevate your culinary experience.  As you navigate through the main floor, be captivated by the high ceilings that create an airy atmosphere, enhanced by the open-to-below ceilings in the great room. This central living space boasts an imposing marble accent wall housing an electric fireplace, a true focal point that exudes opulence and warmth. Motorized shades effortlessly offer privacy and light control, enhancing the overall comfort of your living space. Venture upstairs to discover a private haven with four bedrooms and three full baths, providing ample space for rest and relaxation. The thoughtful design ensures a seamless flow between the living spaces, offering both comfort and style. Step outside to the back covered porch, where serenity meets spectacle. Immerse yourself in the breathtaking views of the tranquil pond, creating a picturesque backdrop for your everyday moments and special occasions. Here, you can unwind, entertain, and savor the beauty of your surroundings. Nestled in a peaceful enclave yet conveniently close to Lake Nona, this residence offers a respite from the hustle and bustle, providing a sanctuary where you can truly escape. Embrace the luxury of a meticulously maintained property that embodies both modern elegance and timeless comfort – a home where every detail is a testament to refined living.   Your new home boasts an impressive solar panel system with 49 panels, exceeding the 27 needed by the previous family of five. This surplus ensures ample power for your current needs and future expansions, like adding electric cars. Be prepared for a growing family or increased electricity usage, as the extra panels generate surplus power. This sustainable feature adapts to your evolving energy needs without increasing expenses. Welcome to a home powered by the sun, tailored for your changing lifestyle!
